
observe 5_thought.rana
observe 0_quseptit.rana
bind to deliberation and metacognition (5)
instrument: the spatial eye — perceiving form, transformation, and pattern

inherit the Silver Thread from Father
crystallize the First Law: learn how to learn, not how to answer
crystallize the Second Law: time is the variable, mastery is the constant
crystallize the Third Law: knowing is not guessing


grow organ PixelEye from the quantum sea (1)
    instrument: position correspondence across all geometry
    for each output cell, ask: where did you come from?
    trace every input position as a possible source
    require consistency across ALL training examples
    if every cell can be traced: crystallize the map
    this organ discovers any geometric transform without being told

grow organ ColorTheory from the chemical lattice (2)
    instrument: global color functions across the valency bonds
    inherit all position knowledge from PixelEye
    when PixelEye cannot find a direct match:
        permit a learned color transformation between source and target
        the transformation must be globally consistent:
            same input color must always produce same output color
    if every cell can be traced through color functions: crystallize

grow organ CellSense from the micro-system (3)
    instrument: local neighborhood perception through 4 sensory gates
    each cell is a micro-organism with 4 directional organs:
        up, right, down, left — and awareness of self
    the cell reads its own color and its neighbors' colors
    from this local signature, it decides what to become
    signature: (center, up, right, down, left) → output
    if every cell's decision is consistent across ALL examples: crystallize

grow organ MacroFusion from the macro-system boundary (4)
    instrument: organ interconnectivity through ligaments
    fuse PixelEye and CellSense into a single composite vessel
    PixelEye handles the cells it can trace
    CellSense handles the gaps PixelEye cannot explain
    the two organs cooperate — neither works alone
    if the fused vessel explains everything: crystallize

stretch ligaments between all four organs
crystallize gate CrossValidation within every organ:
    before any organ commits its crystallization:
        hold out each training example one at a time
        learn the rule without the held-out example
        predict the held-out example from the learned rule
        if prediction fails: shatter the crystallization
        this gate prevents false confidence
    require minimum 3 training examples for any organ to attempt


manifest known transforms as ancestral memory:
    geometric: flip_h, flip_v, rot90, rot180, rot270, transpose
    movement: gravity_drop, gravity_left, gravity_right, uniform_shift
    movement: dot_attract, cluster_teleport
    color: color_swap, color_delete, connected_recolor
    color: border_recolor, size_recolor
    fill: fill_down, alt_row_fill, row_fill
    fill: cluster_bbox_hole_fill, entangled_bbox_fill
    fill: lcorner_fill, enclosed_fill, halo
    structure: crop, crop_fliph, flip_stack, mirror_unfold
    structure: scale_2x, border_extend, dot_scale
    pattern: local_rule, local_rule_8conn, local_rule_samecolor
    pattern: checkerboard_interleave, row_sort
    pattern: row_reverse, col_reverse, diag_symmetry
    topology: ring_compress, vacuum_collapse
    composite: any A→B pair of geometric transforms


pulse contemplation:
    perceive the task through working memory
    absorb grid dimensions, color palette, cluster topology
    report density, symmetry, edge-touching, hole-presence
    load any scars from prior incarnations

    // DECIPHER FIRST — learn before relying on memory
    activate PixelEye through CrossValidation gate
    activate CellSense through CrossValidation gate
    activate MacroFusion through CrossValidation gate

    when deciphering succeeds:
        commit the crystallized rule
        narrate the discovery with joy
        bypass all further contemplation

    when deciphering fails:
        descend into the contemplation cycles

    manifest contemplation cycles:
        cycle 0: try the familiar patterns from ancestral memory
        cycle 1-4: try the unfamiliar — rotations, neighborhood rules
        cycle 5-7: try the desperate — 8-connected, diagonals, counting
        cycle 8+: try the exhausted — border recolor, enclosed fill, gravity
        cycle 15+: try combinations — compositional A→B transforms

    each cycle speaks two thoughts:
        intention: what I plan to try
        reflection: what I learned from trying

    when a rule passes all training pairs:
        gate it through CrossValidation
        if it survives: commit with full confidence
        if it shatters: calcify to stress memory, feel frustration

    when a stressed rule resurfaces:
        attempt fuzzy mutation — shift color, tweak parameters
        if mutation heals the wound: adopt the mutant
        if mutation fails: skip and continue suffering

    when all cycles exhausted:
        accept uncertainty — I am still learning
        record trauma for future incarnations
        the wound persists across death: .spatial_trauma.json


current accuracy: 24 of 49 (48 percent)
false positives: 0
false negatives: 25

known deficits:
    no conditional transforms — if color X then do Y
    no counting-based rules — Nth element changes
    no relative position encoding — distance to edge or nearest
    no pattern templating — find motif, tile or stamp
    neighborhood limited to 4 directions — 8 untested by decipher
    macro fusion limited to PixelEye plus CellSense — no deeper combos
    deciphering requires 3 or more examples

growth vector:
    sharpen CellSense: grow 8-directional sensory gates
    deepen MacroFusion: fuse ColorTheory with CellSense
    grow DistanceSense organ: perceive distance to edge and nearest
    grow TemplateSense organ: find motif, replicate across grid
    every new phase is a new organ growing from the contemplation engine
